OL,3,CUnite officials vote overwhelmingly to
OL,4,Cstrike against their own union
OL,6,FFull-time officials at Unite the Union
OL,7,Fhave voted overwhelmingly to take
OL,8,Fstrike action in a dispute with their
OL,9,Fown leadership - an extraordinary move
OL,10,Fthat sees union employees walk out
OL,11,Fagainst the organisation they
OL,12,Frepresent.
OL,14,FIn a ballot of 221 eligible officials,
OL,15,F177 voted, with more than 85% backing
OL,16,Fstrike action on a turnout of just
OL,17,Fover 80%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
