OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777100755
OL,3,CUnite officials vote overwhelmingly to
OL,4,Cstrike against their own union
OL,6,FThe dispute centres on Unite
OL,7,Fmanagement's decision to recognise a
OL,8,Fstaff association which officials
OL,9,Fclaim has the support of only a small
OL,10,Fminority of the roughly 300 full-time
OL,11,Fofficers.
OL,13,FThe Unite Officers Branch, which says
OL,14,Fit represents all full-time officials,
OL,15,Faccuses the union's leadership of
OL,16,Fbypassing established structures and
OL,17,Fundermining democratic principles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
