PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777100755
OL,3,CUnite officials vote overwhelmingly to
OL,4,Cstrike against their own union
OL,6,FIn a statement, the branch said it
OL,7,Fwould "not accept this with any
OL,8,Femployer", describing the move as a
OL,9,F"union-busting technique" used to
OL,10,Fcircumvent a recognised body.
OL,12,FTalks between the two sides were held
OL,13,Fearlier this week through the
OL,14,FAdvisory, Conciliation and Arbitration
OL,15,FService (Acas).
