CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777100755
OL,3,CUnite officials vote overwhelmingly to
OL,4,Cstrike against their own union
OL,6,FOfficials from the Unite Officers
OL,7,FBranch, who are represented in the
OL,8,Fdispute by the union, Community, say a
OL,9,Fdeal was reached and written up by
OL,10,FAcas but claim Unite management
OL,11,Freneged on the agreement the following
OL,12,Fmorning - an allegation the union
OL,13,Fdisputes.
OL,15,FUnite said the dispute relates only to
OL,16,Fa minority of staff who are members of
OL,17,FCommunity and centres on competing
OL,18,Frepresentation arrangements among its
OL,19,Fofficers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
