PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777100755
OL,3,CUnite officials vote overwhelmingly to
OL,4,Cstrike against their own union
OL,6,FIt said Community had been granted
OL,7,Frecognition on the basis that it would
OL,8,Fnot be the sole representative body,
OL,9,Fin order to protect existing "legacy"
OL,10,Frepresentation for other officials.
OL,12,FUnite accused the Community branch of
OL,13,Fseeking to remove those arrangements,
OL,14,Fand said contingency plans were in
OL,15,Fplace with only limited disruption
OL,16,Fexpected.
